{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L982"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s callout view."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"mapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"annotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UIControl","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)UIControl"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"control"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The map view containing the specified annotation."}]}],"name":"mapView"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation whose accessory view was tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotation"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The control that was tapped.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"control"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In a standard callout view, accessory views contain custom content and are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"positioned on either side of the annotation title text. If an accessory view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you specify is a descendant of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" class, the map view calls this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"type":"text","text":" class,"},{"type":